<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8" />
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
<title>Ora — Your Chart. Your Clarity.</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,500;1,300;1,400&family=DM+Sans:opsz,wght@9..40,300;9..40,400;9..40,500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
<style>
  :root {
    --cream: #FAF8F4;
    --ink: #1A1714;
    --ink-60: rgba(26,23,20,0.6);
    --ink-30: rgba(26,23,20,0.3);
    --ink-10: rgba(26,23,20,0.1);
    --gold: #B8975A;
    --gold-light: #F2EAD9;
    --surface: #F4F1EB;
    --white: #FFFFFF;
    --radius-sm: 8px;
    --radius-md: 14px;
    --radius-lg: 20px;
    --radius-pill: 100px;
  }
  *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
  html, body { height: 100%; width: 100%; background: var(--cream); color: var(--ink); font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; overflow-x: hidden; }
  body::before { content: ''; position: fixed; inset: 0; background-image: radial-gradient(1px 1px at 15% 20%, rgba(184,151,90,0.4) 0%, transparent 100%), radial-gradient(1.5px 1.5px at 72% 15%, rgba(184,151,90,0.5) 0%, transparent 100%), radial-gradient(1px 1px at 88% 30%, rgba(184,151,90,0.3) 0%, transparent 100%), radial-gradient(1.5px 1.5px at 10% 70%, rgba(184,151,90,0.4) 0%, transparent 100%), radial-gradient(1.5px 1.5px at 25% 92%, rgba(184,151,90,0.4) 0%, transparent 100%); pointer-events: none; z-index: 0; }
  .app { position: relative; z-index: 1; min-height: 100vh; display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; justify-content: center; padding: 2rem 1rem; }
  .card { width: 100%; max-width: 520px; background: var(--white); border-radius: var(--radius-lg); border: 1px solid var(--ink-10); overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 2px 40px rgba(26,23,20,0.07); display: flex; flex-direction: column; min-height: 580px; }
  .header { text-align: center; padding: 2rem 1.5rem 1.25rem; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--ink-10); background: var(--white); position: relative; }
  .header::after { content: ''; position: absolute; bottom: -1px; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%); width: 40px; height: 2px; background: var(--gold); }
  .wordmark { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 36px; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: 0.4em; color: var(--ink); text-indent: 0.4em; }
  .tagline { font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 0.18em; color: var(--gold); margin-top: 5px; text-transform: uppercase; }
  .screen { display: none; flex-direction: column; flex: 1; }
  .screen.active { display: flex; }
  .onboard-body { flex: 1; display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; padding: 2rem 1.75rem; gap: 1.5rem; }
  .intro { text-align: center; }
  .intro h2 { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 26px; font-weight: 400; font-style: italic; color: var(--ink); line-height: 1.3; margin-bottom: 0.6rem; }
  .intro p { font-size: 13.5px; color: var(--ink-60); line-height: 1.75; max-width: 340px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .divider { width: 32px; height: 1px; background: var(--gold); opacity: 0.6; }
  .form { width: 100%; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1rem; }
  .field { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 6px; }
  .field-label { font-size: 10.5px; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--ink-60); }
  .field-row { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 12px; }
  input { width: 100%; padding: 11px 14px; border-radius: var(--radius-sm); border: 1px solid var(--ink-10); background: var(--surface); color: var(--ink); font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 14px; }
  input:focus { outline: none; border-color: var(--gold); background: var(--white); }
  input::placeholder { color: var(--ink-30); }
  .btn-primary { width: 100%; padding: 13px; border-radius: var(--radius-sm); border: none; background: var(--ink); color: var(--cream); font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 13.5px; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 0.08em; cursor: pointer; margin-top: 0.25rem; }
  .btn-primary:hover { background: #2E2A26; }
  .error-msg { font-size: 12px; color: #C0392B; text-align: center; padding: 0.4rem 0; }
  .notice { font-size: 11px; color: var(--ink-30); text-align: center; }
  .chart-strip { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; padding: 0.85rem 1rem; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--ink-10); background: var(--surface); flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 0; }
  .chart-planet { display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; gap: 3px; padding: 0 0.85rem; border-right: 1px solid var(--ink-10); }
  .chart-planet:last-child { border-right: none; }
  .planet-label { font-size: 9.5px; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--gold); }
  .planet-value { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 15px; color: var(--ink); white-space: nowrap; }
  .chat-messages { flex: 1; overflow-y: auto; padding: 1.5rem; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1.1rem; min-height: 280px; max-height: 360px; }
  .msg { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 4px; max-width: 90%; animation: fadeUp 0.25s ease both; }
  @keyframes fadeUp { from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(6px); } to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); } }
  .msg.ora { align-self: flex-start; }
  .msg.user { align-self: flex-end; }
  .msg-sender { font-size: 10px; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--ink-30); padding: 0 4px; }
  .msg.user .msg-sender { text-align: right; }
  .bubble { padding: 13px 17px; border-radius: var(--radius-md); line-height: 1.7; border: 1px solid transparent; }
  .msg.ora .bubble { background: var(--gold-light); border-color: rgba(184,151,90,0.2); font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 17px; color: var(--ink); border-radius: var(--radius-md) var(--radius-md) var(--radius-md) 4px; }
  .msg.user .bubble { background: var(--ink); color: var(--cream); font-size: 14px; border-radius: var(--radius-md) var(--radius-md) 4px var(--radius-md); }
  .typing-bubble { display: flex; gap: 5px; align-items: center; padding: 16px 20px; background: var(--gold-light); border: 1px solid rgba(184,151,90,0.2); border-radius: var(--radius-md) var(--radius-md) var(--radius-md) 4px; }
  .dot { width: 7px; height: 7px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--gold); animation: breathe 1.3s ease-in-out infinite; }
  .dot:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 0.2s; }
  .dot:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 0.4s; }
  @keyframes breathe { 0%, 100% { opacity: 0.3; transform: scale(0.75); } 50% { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1); } }
  .chips { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 8px; padding: 0 1.5rem 0.75rem; }
  .chip { padding: 6px 14px; border-radius: var(--radius-pill); border: 1px solid var(--ink-10); background: var(--surface); font-size: 12px; font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; color: var(--ink-60); cursor: pointer; white-space: nowrap; }
  .chip:hover { border-color: var(--gold); color: var(--ink); background: var(--gold-light); }
  .input-area { display: flex; gap: 10px; padding: 0.85rem 1.25rem 1.25rem; border-top: 1px solid var(--ink-10); align-items: flex-end; background: var(--white); }
  textarea { flex: 1; resize: none; padding: 11px 14px; border-radius: var(--radius-md); border: 1px solid var(--ink-10); background: var(--surface); color: var(--ink); font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5; min-height: 44px; max-height: 120px; }
  textarea:focus { outline: none; border-color: var(--gold); background: var(--white); }
  textarea::placeholder { color: var(--ink-30); }
  .send-btn { width: 44px; height: 44px; border-radius: 50%; border: none; background: var(--ink); color: var(--cream); cursor: pointer; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; flex-shrink: 0; }
  .send-btn:hover { opacity: 0.85; }
  .send-btn:disabled { opacity: 0.3; cursor: not-allowed; }
  @media (max-width: 560px) { .app { padding: 0; justify-content: flex-start; } .card { border-radius: 0; min-height: 100svh; } }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="app">
  <div class="card">
    <div class="header">
      <div class="wordmark">ORA</div>
      <div class="tagline">Your chart. Your clarity.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="screen active" id="screen-onboard">
      <div class="onboard-body">
        <div class="intro">
          <h2>Know yourself more clearly.</h2>
          <p>Ora is a real conversation about your actual life — grounded in your birth chart. Not a horoscope. Not a personality quiz.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="divider"></div>
